HEADWORD: Ensearch
<hw>En*search"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>encerchier</ets>. See <er>Search</er>.]</ety> <def>To make search;
to try to find something.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> -- <def2><pos>v.
t.</pos> <def>To search for.</def></def2> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Sir T. Elyot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

